<date box="[435,566,1585,1610]" pageId="16" pageNumber="525" value="1925-10-13">13. x. 1925</date>
; collected by SN Chatterjee'. Label 2: White label stating 'Defoliating 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Urena" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvaceae" pageId="16" pageNumber="525" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sinuata">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="525">Urena sinuata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
'. Label 3: Small label with number '28'. Label 4: a small label with faded number? '6'. Label 5: White label ' 
<taxonomicName authority="Bryant" authorityName="Bryant" box="[156,484,1657,1682]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Podagrica" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="525" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="apicefulva">
<emphasis box="[156,398,1657,1682]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="525">Podagrica apicefulva</emphasis>
Bryant
</taxonomicName>
, Paratype (hand written), det. GE Bryant'. Label 6: Green label stating 'Paratype'.
</paragraph>
